    <section id="intro">
      <div class="cell">
        <p>This is a blogging platform boiled down to its core. The only features are saving drafts, and publishing them.</p>
        <p>The post format is markdown or plain text<sup>1</sup>, use SCP to transfer posts. First line or H1 is the title.</p>
        <p>It serves posts under your <a href="/~postmaster" target="_blank">~username</a>, which is the only thing it knows about you, aside from SSH key or password authentication.</p>
        <p>
          Simple and <a href="https://www.eff.org/issues/anonymity" target="_blank">anonymous</a>.
        </p>
        <hr>
        <p style="font-size:.75em;color:grey">1: [link format https://weblog.sh], this is the web after all</p>
      </div>
    </section>

